Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:37.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最新卷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:41.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我等好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:45.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,购物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,妈妈要去买东西 买完了就来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要买太花哨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:05.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,百分百单相思的最新卷
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要买什么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他喜欢什么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,赶紧回家看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么那么惊讶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:21.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 为什么总是这么不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道她在跟踪我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:28.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 总之现在不是害怕的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:31.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不能让她知道我买的是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 你刚从书店出来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你买了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得想个方法转移话题混过去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我来买泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:04.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的脸好红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 是因为太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:08.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片喜欢什么样的泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你问什么样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么样的都行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说只要是泳衣就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的意思是对这个没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很热吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很热
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才见面一会儿就成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没事的话我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:37.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:41.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 好歹把漫画给保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你今天买的百分百单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下次借给我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:03.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在外面应该看不到收银台才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她在虚张声势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,差点就中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是啦 不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你买了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:20.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,机…机器人僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:33.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样 女生对这个完全没兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没兴趣就快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:41.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其实是百分百单相思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才 才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那让我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又…又被她逼上绝路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到头来还是变成这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:59.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我会被高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们打个赌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:10.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:17.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,赌我买的书究竟是不是百分百单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是高木同学猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就要答应我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:28.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我猜对了 你也要答应我一件事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没问题 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你要猜哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我这光明磊落的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心里肯定疑惑不解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:46.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 西片竟然会这么堂堂正正的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:51.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说不是百分百单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:53.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正也会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就让高木同学也尝尝苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我和之前不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也是每天都在成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我赌是百分百单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:10.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 我猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么我会遇上这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,赶紧回家 看看漫画治愈一下心灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来帮我挑泳衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不是说如果我赢了就答应我一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:54.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很热吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:07:59.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你觉得哪件比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪件都挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给我认真一点选啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为西片输了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,光是呆在这里就够羞耻的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪还能直视泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看看 这件怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然如此 那就赶紧选了走人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:41.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我去试穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:51.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以跑到别的地方去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么我会碰上这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在那块布的对面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不…不知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我继续试穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要试穿到你说合适为止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这种做作的话怎么说出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 能帮我拿一下泳衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那里右边的那件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道高木同学现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那一件再往左边数一件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是那一件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在 在布的另一端…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一定是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:32.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的不尽快选好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是在这种地方被同级生看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知道会被他们怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有很多种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 这件怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 高木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有中井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哦 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们来买泳衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}疼疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 这里太羞耻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快点选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家想好好挑一件喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们待会再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待会见 高木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真野和中井他们走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你也太害羞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还要继续试穿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是时候该决定买哪一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为西片太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都说了我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:26.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你觉得哪一件更好看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,两件都挺好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:33.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么这件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:36.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样 你觉得合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那这件粉色的好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:46.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这件连体的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下次一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:51.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:55.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待会我请你喝果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:05.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看上去好像很热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:10.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真的好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,夏天到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,裙带菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,别这样 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看了就知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在给游泳圈打气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不先去游一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以我就是为了去游泳才打气的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 你不会游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:14.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怪不得你上游泳课时老请假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:17.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,别管了 你们先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,游了个爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,先休息一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:47.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:50.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,打气泵坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:54.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接用嘴吹气累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉有在好好地享受人生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,少管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我再也不帮你做暑假作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你自己做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,唯有那件事还请放我一马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:16.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你做暑假作业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:32.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 做了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不今天一起做作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我中午之后有约了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那中午之前一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可以把作业借给你抄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我们在哪里做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去图书馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是回去拿作业也要花不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去西片家做不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:12.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:18.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学突然要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女生要来我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍等一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用太拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我爸妈都在上班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这不是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学来到了我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太没有现实感了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看你一直在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:04.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是百分百单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你居然把全套买齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,别看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:19.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:24.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你喜欢对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喜欢的话直接说喜欢不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,两人独处的时候说这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我该怎么回答才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这果然是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,百分百单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:46.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用藏着掖着也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来在说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的房间很有西片的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这是在赞我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没在赞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然我很喜欢就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们来做作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:20.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说我只有一张桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有没有可折叠的那种矮桌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:31.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,全都放在别的房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我们要挤在一张椅子上做作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们去床上做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把被子移开就能当做桌子用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:07.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:14.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那来吧 来做作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 我也要去那里做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:30.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 关于你刚才说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,当然 我会遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过我只带了汉字的练字册而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 你骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才没有骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来做作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:05.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是练字的话 根本没必要专门一起做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:25.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,百分百单相思里见过的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:34.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 为什么我非得和这种人一起做咖喱不可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我怎么会放手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:56.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是西片的橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:01.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:04.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:07.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你渴不渴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喝麦茶行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:13.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:45.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉一直在被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「还会来的」？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去收拾一下房间吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:15.72,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:20.14,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:30.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:39.28,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:47.58,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:55.92,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:59.80,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.72,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:11.81,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:20.11,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:25.54,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:29.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:39.76,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:15.72,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:20.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:30.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:39.28,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:47.58,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:55.92,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:59.80,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.72,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:11.81,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:20.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:25.54,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:29.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:39.76,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:12.81,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言って努力は嫌いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:18.73,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言って人は人だね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.74,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどなぜ窓ガラスに映る姿気にしてるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:32.16,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどなぜ意地になって　移る流行気にしてるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:38.67,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}はっきり言ってお伽話は罠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:44.76,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}期待したってカボチャはカボチャ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:51.60,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどもうダメみたいだ　何だか近頃おかしいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:58.90,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だけどもうダメみたいだ　何だか近頃おかしいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:02.65,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}走り出した足が止まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.95,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}行け　行け　あの人のところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:09.78,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}誰にも抜かれたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:13.12,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風　風　背中を押してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}足が止まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.87,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}行け　行け　あの人のところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:22.63,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}誰にも負けたくないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:26.30,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風　風　背中を押してよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:12.81,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}说实话 我最讨厌的就是努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:18.73,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}说实话 别人就是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.74,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但为什么我会在意自己映在玻璃窗上的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:32.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但为什么意气用事地在意着不断变化的流行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:38.67,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}说实话 童话故事都是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:44.76,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}就算如何期待 南瓜也还是南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:51.60,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但好像有点不行了 感觉最近的自己有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:58.90,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}但好像有点不行了 感觉最近的自己有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.90,0:23:02.65,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}疾驰的脚步无法停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.95,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}去吧 去吧 到那个人的身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:09.78,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不希望被任何人超越
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:13.12,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿 风儿 助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:15.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}脚步无法停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.87,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}去吧 去吧 到那个人的身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.87,0:23:22.63,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不希望输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:26.30,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿 风儿 助我一臂之力
